---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import CtaSection from '../components/CtaSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Online Therapist for San Francisco | EMDR & Trauma | Maren Voss"
  description="EMDR and trauma therapy for San Francisco residents via secure telehealth. Specializing in anxiety, burnout, and high-achiever stress."
>
  <Header slot="header" />

  <section class="interior-hero section-dark section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="heading-page">Online Therapy for San Francisco Residents</h1>
      <p class="interior-hero__tagline">Oakland-based therapist, available across the Bay via telehealth.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-cream section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="body-text fade-in-up">
        <p>I work with a number of clients in San Francisco who prefer telehealth over commuting to the East Bay. Secure video sessions offer the same quality of care as in-person work, and for many people, the convenience of logging on from home or a private office actually makes them more consistent with therapy.</p>
        <p>San Francisco's professional landscape produces a specific kind of stress. The pace, the cost of living, the culture of optimization, the pressure to perform in tech and startup environments while somehow maintaining a balanced life. Many of my SF clients found their way to me because they were looking for a therapist who understands that world from the inside, not from a textbook.</p>
        <p>If you're in San Francisco and looking for EMDR therapy, trauma-informed care, or a therapist who works with anxiety and burnout in high-achievers, I'd welcome a conversation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-dark section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="body-text fade-in-up">
        <p>I specialize in <a href="/trauma-ptsd" class="text-link-dark">trauma & PTSD</a>, <a href="/anxiety" class="text-link-dark">anxiety</a>, <a href="/burnout" class="text-link-dark">burnout and high-achiever stress</a>, <a href="/relationship-patterns" class="text-link-dark">relationship patterns</a>, and <a href="/life-transitions" class="text-link-dark">life transitions</a>. My approach integrates EMDR, IFS, and somatic therapy.</p>
        <p><a href="/how-i-work" class="text-link-dark">Learn more about how I work &rarr;</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-cream section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="geo-info">
        <div class="geo-info__item">
          <h2 class="heading-sub">Telehealth</h2>
          <p>All sessions are conducted via secure video through SimplePractice. You can connect from anywhere in California.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="geo-info__item">
          <h2 class="heading-sub">In-Person Option</h2>
          <p>My Oakland office (Rockridge, one block from BART) is approximately 25 minutes from downtown SF via BART. Some clients come in person for EMDR sessions and do regular check-ins via video.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="geo-info__item">
          <h2 class="heading-sub">Getting Started</h2>
          <p><a href="/contact" class="text-link-light">Schedule a free 15-minute consultation &rarr;</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaSection />
  <Footer slot="footer" />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .interior-hero {
    position: relative;
    background: url('/images/textures/san-francisco-hero.webp') center / cover no-repeat;
  }
  .interior-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.91);
  }
  .interior-hero .container {
    position: relative;
  }

  .body-text p {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .body-text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .geo-info {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px 64px;
    max-width: var(--content-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .geo-info__item h2 {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .geo-info__item p {
    font-size: var(--body-small);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1023px) {
    .geo-info {
      gap: 40px 48px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .geo-info {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
  }
</style>
<script src="../scripts/scroll-animations.js"></script>
